title: Jefferson National Expansion Memorial: St. Louis in 1804
body: St. Louis in 1804                         St. Louis in 1804 Walkthrough Take a walk through 1804 St. Louis! Park Historian Bob Moore created this model of the town of St. Louis in 1804 in Google SketchUp and now you can enjoy this walking tour through the model. You'll see some of the French style houses and take a walk out to the mounds at the edge of the city.   Duration:8 minutes, 52 seconds           Â     St. Louis in 1804 map. Move your cursor to select the part of the map you'd like to see in greater detail. Bob Moore, National Park Service
